<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>GA4 + GSC — JEGS SKU Enrichment (Pre-click + Post-click)</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.js"></script>
<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#f8f9fa;
    --surface:#ffffff;
    --border:#e8eaed;
    --border-strong:#dadce0;
    --text:#202124;
    --text-muted:#5f6368;
    --text-faint:#80868b;
    --blue:#1a73e8;
    --blue-bg:#e8f0fe;
    --green:#188038;
    --green-bg:#e6f4ea;
    --red:#c5221f;
    --red-bg:#fce8e6;
    --amber:#b06000;
    --amber-bg:#fef7e0;
    --purple:#7627bb;
    --purple-bg:#f3e8fd;
    --gsc:#34a853;
    --gsc-bg:#e6f4ea;
    --ga4:#f9ab00;
    --ga4-bg:#fef7e0;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);font-family:'Google Sans','Roboto',-apple-system,Segoe UI,sans-serif;color:var(--text);font-size:13px;line-height:1.5}

  /* Top bar */
  .topbar{background:#fff;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:8px 20px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:20}
  .ga-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:18px;font-weight:500}
  .ga-logo .dot{width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f9ab00 0%,#e8710a 100%)}
  .source-pills{display:flex;gap:6px}
  .source-pill{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:12px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;border:1px solid}
  .source-pill.ga4{background:var(--ga4-bg);color:var(--amber);border-color:#fde293}
  .source-pill.gsc{background:var(--gsc-bg);color:var(--gsc);border-color:#a8dab5}
  .source-pill i{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;background:currentColor}
  .property{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:6px 12px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted)}
  .property strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:500}
  .topbar-spacer{flex:1}
  .topbar-btn{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:#e8eaed;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:12px;font-weight:500}

  .shell{display:grid;grid-template-columns:240px 1fr;min-height:calc(100vh - 53px)}
  .sidebar{background:#fff;border-right:1px solid var(--border);padding:12px 0;font-size:13px}
  .nav-section{padding:4px 0}
  .nav-title{padding:8px 24px 4px;color:var(--text-faint);font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.8px;font-weight:500}
  .nav-item{padding:8px 24px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;color:var(--text-muted);border-left:3px solid transparent}
  .nav-item:hover{background:#f1f3f4;color:var(--text)}
  .nav-item.active{background:var(--blue-bg);color:var(--blue);border-left-color:var(--blue);font-weight:500}
  .nav-icon{width:14px;height:14px;display:inline-block;flex-shrink:0}
  .badge-new{display:inline-block;background:var(--gsc-bg);color:var(--gsc);font-size:9px;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:500;margin-left:auto}

  .main{padding:20px 28px 60px;min-width:0;overflow-x:hidden}

  .page-head{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;margin-bottom:20px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .page-head h1{font-size:22px;font-weight:400;margin:0 0 4px}
  .breadcrumb{color:var(--text-faint);font-size:12px;margin-bottom:6px}
  .date-pill{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 14px;border:1px solid var(--border-strong);border-radius:4px;background:#fff;font-size:13px}

  .filters{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:16px;padding:10px 12px;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;align-items:center}
  .filter-chip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:5px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border-strong);border-radius:16px;background:#fff;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted)}
  .filter-chip.active{background:var(--blue-bg);border-color:#a8c7fa;color:var(--blue)}
  .filter-chip.gsc-chip{background:var(--gsc-bg);border-color:#a8dab5;color:var(--gsc)}
  .filter-chip.ga4-chip{background:var(--ga4-bg);border-color:#fde293;color:var(--amber)}
  .filter-chip .x{color:var(--text-faint);font-weight:600}
  .filter-add{color:var(--blue);cursor:pointer;font-weight:500;padding:5px 10px;font-size:12px}

  /* Scorecards split by source */
  .source-section{margin-bottom:20px}
  .source-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:10px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
  .source-header h3{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;margin:0;color:var(--text)}
  .source-header .tag{font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-weight:500;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:10px}
  .source-header.gsc .tag{background:var(--gsc-bg);color:var(--gsc)}
  .source-header.ga4 .tag{background:var(--ga4-bg);color:var(--amber)}
  .source-header .desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-left:auto}

  .scorecards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:12px}
  .scorecard{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;position:relative}
  .scorecard.gsc{border-top:3px solid var(--gsc)}
  .scorecard.ga4{border-top:3px solid var(--ga4)}
  .scorecard .label{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);font-weight:500;margin-bottom:4px}
  .scorecard .value{font-size:24px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.3px}
  .scorecard .delta{font-size:12px;margin-top:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px}
  .delta.up{color:var(--green)}
  .delta.down{color:var(--red)}
  .delta.flat{color:var(--text-faint)}

  .card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:16px}
  .card-head{padding:14px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
  .card-head h2{font-size:14px;font-weight:500;margin:0}
  .card-head .sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:2px}
  .card-body{padding:16px}
  .card-actions{display:flex;gap:12px;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:12px}
  .card-actions a{color:var(--blue);cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none}

  .two-col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:16px}

  .chart-wrap{position:relative;width:100%;height:260px}
  .chart-wrap.tall{height:320px}
  .chart-wrap.short{height:200px}

  /* Quadrant chart wrapper — needs padding so bubbles don't clip */
  .quad-wrap{position:relative;height:380px;padding:8px}

  /* Tables */
  table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12px}
  thead th{text-align:left;padding:10px 10px;color:var(--text-muted);font-weight:500;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.4px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-strong);background:#fafafa;cursor:pointer;user-select:none;white-space:nowrap}
  thead th:hover{background:#f1f3f4;color:var(--text)}
  thead th.num{text-align:right}
  thead th.sorted::after{content:'▼';margin-left:4px;color:var(--blue);font-size:9px}
  thead th.group-gsc{background:var(--gsc-bg);color:var(--gsc);border-bottom-color:var(--gsc)}
  thead th.group-ga4{background:var(--ga4-bg);color:var(--amber);border-bottom-color:var(--ga4)}
  tbody td{padding:9px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);vertical-align:middle}
  tbody td.num{text-align:right;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
  tbody td.gsc-col{background:rgba(230,244,234,0.25)}
  tbody td.ga4-col{background:rgba(254,247,224,0.25)}
  tbody tr:hover td{background:#f8f9fa}
  tbody tr:hover td.gsc-col{background:#e6f4ea}
  tbody tr:hover td.ga4-col{background:var(--ga4-bg)}
  .sku-cell{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
  .sku-thumb{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:4px;background:var(--bg);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);flex-shrink:0;border:1px solid var(--border)}
  .sku-main{min-width:0}
  .sku-id{font-family:'Roboto Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--text-muted)}
  .sku-name{font-size:12px;color:var(--text);font-weight:500;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;max-width:240px}

  .badge{display:inline-block;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.3px}
  .badge.high{background:var(--red-bg);color:var(--red)}
  .badge.med{background:var(--amber-bg);color:var(--amber)}
  .badge.low{background:var(--green-bg);color:var(--green)}
  .badge.critical{background:#5b1411;color:#fcd8d5}
  .badge.cat{background:var(--purple-bg);color:var(--purple)}

  .mini-bar{width:60px;height:5px;background:var(--bg);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:4px}
  .mini-bar .fill{height:100%;border-radius:3px}
  .mini-bar .fill.blue{background:var(--blue)}
  .mini-bar .fill.red{background:var(--red)}
  .mini-bar .fill.amber{background:var(--amber)}
  .mini-bar .fill.green{background:var(--green)}
  .mini-bar .fill.gsc{background:var(--gsc)}

  .pos-indicator{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
  .pos-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block}

  /* Tabs */
  .tabs{display:flex;gap:0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:16px;overflow-x:auto}
  .tab{padding:10px 16px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);cursor:pointer;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;font-weight:500;white-space:nowrap}
  .tab.active{color:var(--blue);border-bottom-color:var(--blue)}
  .tab:hover:not(.active){color:var(--text);background:#f8f9fa}

  /* Pagination */
  .pagination{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:12px 16px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted)}
  .pager-btns{display:flex;gap:4px}
  .pager-btn{padding:4px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border-strong);border-radius:3px;background:#fff;cursor:pointer;font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted)}
  .pager-btn:disabled{opacity:0.4;cursor:not-allowed}
  .pager-btn.current{background:var(--blue);color:#fff;border-color:var(--blue)}

  .callout{background:var(--blue-bg);border-left:3px solid var(--blue);padding:12px 16px;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:13px;color:#174ea6}
  .callout strong{color:var(--blue)}

  .legend{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px;font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted)}
  .legend-sq{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
  .legend-sq i{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:2px;display:inline-block}

  /* Quadrant legend */
  .quad-info{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:8px;margin-top:12px}
  .quad-cell{padding:10px;border-radius:6px;font-size:11px;line-height:1.4}
  .quad-cell strong{font-size:12px;display:block;margin-bottom:3px}
  .quad-cell.critical{background:var(--red-bg);color:var(--red)}
  .quad-cell.gsc-only{background:var(--gsc-bg);color:var(--gsc)}
  .quad-cell.ga4-only{background:var(--ga4-bg);color:var(--amber)}
  .quad-cell.healthy{background:#f1f3f4;color:var(--text-muted)}

  /* Priority pill */
  .priority-pill{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.3px}
  .priority-pill.p1{background:#5b1411;color:#fcd8d5}
  .priority-pill.p2{background:var(--red-bg);color:var(--red)}
  .priority-pill.p3{background:var(--amber-bg);color:var(--amber)}
  .priority-pill.p4{background:var(--green-bg);color:var(--green)}

  /* Split card with two sections */
  .dual-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:16px;overflow:hidden}
  .dual-card-head{padding:14px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
  .dual-card-body{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;min-height:280px}
  .dual-section{padding:14px 16px}
  .dual-section:first-child{border-right:1px solid var(--border);background:rgba(230,244,234,0.15)}
  .dual-section:last-child{background:rgba(254,247,224,0.15)}
  .dual-section-head{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:10px}
  .dual-section-head .tag{font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-weight:500;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:10px}
  .dual-section-head .tag.gsc{background:var(--gsc-bg);color:var(--gsc)}
  .dual-section-head .tag.ga4{background:var(--ga4-bg);color:var(--amber)}
  .dual-section-head h4{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;margin:0}

  .footer-note{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-faint);text-align:center;padding:20px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:24px}

  .reconcile-note{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-faint);padding:8px 12px;background:#fafafa;border:1px dashed var(--border-strong);border-radius:4px;margin-top:10px}
  .reconcile-note strong{color:var(--text-muted)}

  /* Query table within SKU drill-down */
  .query-table{font-size:11px}
  .query-table td{padding:6px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f3f4}
  .query-table .q{color:var(--text);font-family:'Roboto Mono',monospace;font-size:11px}
  .query-table .imp{color:var(--text-muted);text-align:right;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}

  /* Flex row */
  .kpi-row{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .kpi{flex:1;min-width:140px}

  /* Icons */
  .icn{width:18px;height:18px;display:inline-block;position:relative;flex-shrink:0}
  .icn-home::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:3px;border:1.5px solid currentColor;border-radius:2px;border-top:none}
  .icn-home::after{content:'';position:absolute;left:3px;right:3px;top:3px;height:4px;border:1.5px solid currentColor;border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;clip-path:polygon(50% 0%, 100% 100%, 0% 100%)}
  .icn-bar{background:linear-gradient(to top,currentColor 30%,transparent 30%) 0 100%/4px 50% no-repeat,linear-gradient(to top,currentColor 60%,transparent 60%) 50% 100%/4px 80% no-repeat,linear-gradient(to top,currentColor 40%,transparent 40%) 100% 100%/4px 65% no-repeat}
  .icn-ecom{border:1.5px solid currentColor;border-radius:2px 2px 4px 4px;box-shadow:inset 0 4px 0 -2px currentColor}
  .icn-sku{border:1.5px solid currentColor;border-radius:2px;background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,currentColor 0 1.5px,transparent 1.5px 4px) center/70% 50% no-repeat}
  .icn-search{width:14px;height:14px;border:1.5px solid currentColor;border-radius:50%;position:relative}
  .icn-search::after{content:'';position:absolute;width:6px;height:1.5px;background:currentColor;right:-4px;bottom:-1px;transform:rotate(45deg)}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Top bar -->
<div class="topbar">
  <div class="ga-logo"><span class="dot"></span> Analytics <span style="color:var(--text-faint);font-weight:400;font-size:13px;margin-left:4px">+ Search Console</span></div>
  <div class="property"><span>All accounts ›</span> <strong>JEGS Performance</strong></div>
  <div class="source-pills">
    <span class="source-pill ga4"><i></i>GA4 connected</span>
    <span class="source-pill gsc"><i></i>GSC connected</span>
  </div>
  <div class="topbar-spacer"></div>
  <div class="topbar-btn">JS</div>
</div>

<div class="shell">

  <aside class="sidebar">
    <div class="nav-section">
      <div class="nav-item"><span class="icn icn-home"></span> Home</div>
      <div class="nav-item"><span class="icn icn-bar"></span> Reports</div>
      <div class="nav-item"><span class="icn icn-ecom"></span> Monetization</div>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-section">
      <div class="nav-title">Acquisition</div>
      <div class="nav-item"><span class="icn icn-search"></span> Search Console</div>
      <div class="nav-item"><span class="icn icn-bar"></span> Traffic acquisition</div>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-section">
      <div class="nav-title">Custom</div>
      <div class="nav-item active"><span class="icn icn-sku"></span> SKU enrichment <span class="badge-new">UPDATED</span></div>
      <div class="nav-item"><span class="icn icn-bar"></span> Catalog coverage</div>
      <div class="nav-item"><span class="icn icn-search"></span> Query gap analysis</div>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <main class="main">

    <div class="page-head">
      <div>
        <div class="breadcrumb">Custom › SKU enrichment › <strong>Pre-click + post-click view</strong></div>
        <h1>SKU enrichment — GSC × GA4 joined analysis</h1>
        <div style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:13px">Discoverability (GSC) and conversion (GA4) side-by-side for the top 500 SKUs. Priority = weakness on both sides.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="date-pill">Mar 17 – Apr 15, 2026 ▾</div>
    </div>

    <div class="filters">
      <span style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:12px;margin-right:4px">Filters:</span>
      <span class="filter-chip gsc-chip">GSC: Impressions ≥ 500 <span class="x">×</span></span>
      <span class="filter-chip ga4-chip">GA4: PDP sessions ≥ 200 <span class="x">×</span></span>
      <span class="filter-chip active">Joined opportunity score &lt; 70 <span class="x">×</span></span>
      <span class="filter-chip">Brand: All <span class="x">▾</span></span>
      <span class="filter-chip">Category: All <span class="x">▾</span></span>
      <span class="filter-add">+ Add filter</span>
      <div style="flex:1"></div>
      <span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-faint)">GSC refresh: 2 days lag · GA4: 14 min ago</span>
    </div>

    <div class="callout">
      <strong>How to read this.</strong> Each SKU now has two scores: a <strong>Discoverability score</strong> from GSC (impressions × CTR gap × position) and a <strong>Conversion score</strong> from GA4 (view→cart × cart→purchase × revenue potential). The combined priority ranks SKUs weak on both sides — these are where enrichment delivers compounding returns. Of 500 SKUs, <strong>138 are weak in both</strong> (P1 critical), 142 GSC-only, 128 GA4-only, 92 mostly healthy.
    </div>

    <!-- GSC scorecards -->
    <div class="source-section">
      <div class="source-header gsc">
        <span class="tag">Google Search Console</span>
        <h3>Pre-click: discoverability</h3>
        <div class="desc">What happens on Google before the visitor arrives</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scorecards">
        <div class="scorecard gsc">
          <div class="label">Total impressions (500 SKUs)</div>
          <div class="value">4.82M</div>
          <div class="delta up">▲ 6.1% vs prev. 30d</div>
        </div>
        <div class="scorecard gsc">
          <div class="label">Total clicks</div>
          <div class="value">96.3K</div>
          <div class="delta down">▼ CTR 2.0% (benchmark 3.4%)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="scorecard gsc">
          <div class="label">Avg. position</div>
          <div class="value">18.7</div>
          <div class="delta down">▼ 2.3 positions — declining</div>
        </div>
        <div class="scorecard gsc">
          <div class="label">Queries without click</div>
          <div class="value">3,420</div>
          <div class="delta flat">High-impression, zero-click terms</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- GA4 scorecards -->
    <div class="source-section">
      <div class="source-header ga4">
        <span class="tag">Google Analytics 4</span>
        <h3>Post-click: conversion</h3>
        <div class="desc">What happens on the PDP after the visitor arrives</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scorecards">
        <div class="scorecard ga4">
          <div class="label">PDP sessions (500 SKUs)</div>
          <div class="value">1.24M</div>
          <div class="delta up">▲ 4.2%</div>
        </div>
        <div class="scorecard ga4">
          <div class="label">Avg. view→cart rate</div>
          <div class="value">2.9%</div>
          <div class="delta down">▼ vs 7.2% catalog avg</div>
        </div>
        <div class="scorecard ga4">
          <div class="label">Revenue (30d)</div>
          <div class="value">$487K</div>
          <div class="delta up">▲ 3.1%</div>
        </div>
        <div class="scorecard ga4">
          <div class="label">Projected annual lift</div>
          <div class="value" style="color:var(--green)">$3.21M</div>
          <div class="delta up">▲ if enriched</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reconcile-note">
        <strong>Note on source reconciliation:</strong> GSC reports 96.3K clicks from Google organic; GA4 reports 112.4K organic sessions on the same URLs. The 14% gap is normal — attribution differences, cross-device sessions, and includes Google Images/Discover not in the GSC default view.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tabs">
      <div class="tab active">Joined opportunity</div>
      <div class="tab">GSC signals</div>
      <div class="tab">GA4 signals</div>
      <div class="tab">Top 500 SKUs</div>
      <div class="tab">Query gaps</div>
      <div class="tab">Funnel diagnostics</div>
    </div>

    <!-- THE QUADRANT: GSC vs GA4 -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-head">
        <div>
          <h2>Discoverability × Conversion — the enrichment priority quadrant</h2>
